lemma_key":"تَبِيع","root":"تبع","pos":"N","occurrence_count":1},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":2,"pos_tags":["noun","verb"],"has_etymology":false,"sense_count":5},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n3736"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%AA%D9%8E%D8%A8%D9%90%D9%8A%D8%B9"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to sell (to agree to transfer goods or provide services)","tags":["ditransitive","transitive"],"examples":[{"text":"بَاعَ زَيْدٌ مَتَاعَهُ.","english":"Zayd sold his possessions."},{"text":"بَاعَنِي بَعْضَ الْأَثَاثِ.","english":"He sold me some furniture."}]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"a linear measure derived from the distance between the two outspread arms of a man – which is mostly equal to his height, a قَامَة (qāma), a fathom, about 180 centimetres"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"the body, including the limbs","examples":[{"text":"رَجُلٌ طَوِيلُ البَاعِ","english":"a man tall of body"}]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"the arms (especially when extended to their full reach)"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"reach, power, ability, eminence, nobility, honour, generosity","examples":[{"text":"هُوَ قَصِيرُ البَاعِ","english":"He is lacking in power or ability, he is stingy"},{"text":"لَهُ فِي ٱلْمَجْدِ سَابِقَةٌ وَبَاعُ","english":"He has precedence and eminence in glory, honour, dignity, or nobility"}]}]},"etymology":null,"ipa":["/baː.ʕa/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n3736","headword_ar":"تَبِيعٌ","root":"tbE","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"[One who is"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"prosecuted,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"sued,"},{"kind":"text","text":"for a right, or due; of the measure"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"faEiylN","text_ar":"فَعِيلٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"in the sense of the measure"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mafoEuwlN","text_ar":"مَفْعُولٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", from"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"tabiEotuhu biHaq~iY","text_ar":"تَبِعْتُهُ بِحَقِّى"},{"kind":"text","text":";] one"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"who owes property to another,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K, TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and whom the latter prosecutes,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"sues, for it."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.)       -A2-  The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"young one of a cow in the first year;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, Msb, K;) so says Aboo-Fak'as El-Asadee: (TA:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"that is a year old;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Az, Mgh, TA;) not so called until he has completed the year; erroneously said by Lth to signify"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a calf ripening to his perfect state:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Az, TA:) thus called because he yet follows his mother; (Mgh, Msb;) the word in this sense being of the measure"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"faEiylN","text_ar":"فَعِيلٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"in the sense of the measure"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"faAEilN","text_ar":"فَاعِلٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (Msb:) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"tiboEN","text_ar":"تِبْعٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifies the same: (TA:) fem. of the former with"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"p","text_ar":"ة"},{"kind":"text","text":": (S, Msb, K:) pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"tibaAEN","text_ar":"تِبَاعٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"tabaAy^iEN","text_ar":"تَبَايِعٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (AA, S, O, K;) both pls. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"tabiyEN","text_ar":"تَبِيعٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (AA, S, O;) or the former is pl. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"tabiyEapN","text_ar":"تَبِيعَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (Msb;) and the pl. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"tabiyEN","text_ar":"تَبِيعٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^atobiEapN","text_ar":"اَتْبِعَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[a pl. of pauc.]; (L, Msb;) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^ataAbiEu","text_ar":"اَتَابِعُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^ataAbiyEu","text_ar":"اَتَابِيعُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", the latter of which is extr., are pls. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^atobiEapN","text_ar":"اَتْبِعَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (L:) the pl. of ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"tiboEN","text_ar":"تِبْعٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"in the abovementioned sense is"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^atobaAEN","text_ar":"اَتْبَاعٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (TA.) Accord. to EshShaabee, (IF,) One"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"whose horns and ears are equal"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in length"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: (IF, K:) but this is a judicial explanation; not deduced from the rules of lexicology. (IF.) ―         -b2-"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I. q."},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"taAbiEN","text_ar":"تَابِعٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"[as signifying One"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"who prosecutes,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"sues,"},{"kind":"text","text":"for a right, or due; and particularly for blood-revenge]. (S, K.) Hence the saying in the Kur [xvii. 71],"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"vum~a laA tajiduwA lakumo","text_ar":"ثُمَّ لَا تَجِدُوا لَكُمْ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EalayonaA bihi tabiyEFA","text_ar":"عَلَيْنَا بِهِ تَبِيعًا"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Then ye shall not find for you any to prosecute for blood-revenge, nor any to sue, against us therein:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Fr. S, K:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"ye shall not find for you any to sue us for the disallowing of what hath befallen you, nor for our averting it from you:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Zj:) [or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"any aider against us;"},{"kind":"text","text":"for]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"tabiyEN","text_ar":"تَبِيعٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"also signifies"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"an aider;"},{"kind":"text","text":"and especially"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"against an enemy."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Lth, K.) ―         -b3-  See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"taAbiEN","text_ar":"تَابِعٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", latter half."}],"source_refs":["S","K","TA","Az","Msb","L","IF","Zj"]}]}}